711ab0e5205c","tid":2414942,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"仲以為仆街38號笠左水<br />\n去左校園台？<br />\n<br />\n４０幾歐野仲去校園台做乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"係，黎搞我常駐個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"邊個<br />\n<br />\n你俾人屌五毛喎好似"},{"pid":"c5d5ac4671594c93f6de4aa45e718c5b52b242d3","tid":2414942,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"250bd8a8fe213b07c4f7446ae7fcacd668400e92","tid":2414942,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T21:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完，入過校台追 post 得交加街條懵撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">搬石頭張六常，PR 網軍專門發佈 BNO 假消息、分化 BNO 手足 及 國際線，見字勿回，感謝。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據如下：</ins><br />\n<br />\n====搬石頭張六常 [常駐：校園台]====<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/36383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/36383</a><br />\n<br />\nPOST 1: [時間已證明六常是對的] BNO 苦 主 後 悔 移 英 ： 返 唔 到 香 港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2385148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2385148</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用英國資薪水平，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實英國最低工資水平遠高於香港，而且藍白領工種之間工資差距水平極低，尊重不同行業。雖然稅收較香港高，但同時有全民醫療同退休保障，長遠生活成本較香港低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPOST 2: 如果你自問學歷差冇經驗冇錢冇乜體力又想要舒服日子，建議留返香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2387307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2387307</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用英國工作機會攻擊英國，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實現時英國失業率較香港低，因為封城反而帶旺部份行業需求，另外英國疫苗注射效率極高，長遠英國工作機會因為武肺問題消退及脫歐人口流失而大幅提升</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPOST 3: [勸世2] 英國滿歧視，移民屬不智<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2378847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2378847</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用外國人會歧視人攻擊英國，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實英國英國本身已經有大量第一二代移民，甚至國家重要官員唔少都係移民後代<br />\n最近英國更有大量協助港人既組織相繼成立：e.g. <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2405905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2405905</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 此人同時擔任分化國際線既工作<br />\n攬炒巴 + 重光團隊只係可有可無嘅人，炒作兩條蛋散係冇咩價值<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380384</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">拉</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSORUCE:<br />\n請問張六常(欣客)(狗隻#36383)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2325823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2325823</a>"},{"pid":"de6b5bbfc6c8b3e2d66bc6533b32488b264c4724","tid":2414942,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"667501aa796cc27f6fe0bd8795cd711ab0e5205c","tid":2414942,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"仲以為仆街38號笠左水<br />\n去左校園台？<br />\n<br />\n４０幾歐野仲去校園台做乜鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">著名白兵打手 母看沸鹽<br />\n借意挑釁，離間陣營團結<br />\n又專門 discredit 其它 KOL<br />\n等條契弟單機就得，見字勿回，感謝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據如下：</ins><br />\n<br />\n<ins>手足比人 DQ 就落井下石，走去吹噓白兵：</ins><br />\n<br />\n３５＋計劃大成功，係時候為白兵平反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2132084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2132084</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>47 人比人拉唔比人去聲援：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【緊急】民陣又緊急呼籲香港人對全港最大忠誠反對派既忠誠度！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2426768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2426768</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>幫手洗白共匪熱狗鄭松泰：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【立場分析】假設，鄭松泰有參加35+，如果鄭松泰係第４８位被捕者，鄭松泰應唔應該繼續俾連登仔怒屌？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2442666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2442666</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>泛民比人拉，繼續落井下石：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【非分化】今日係連登吹奏過黃碧雲既，你地無資格講民主！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2427125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2427125</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>誤導人攻擊泛民：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【理性分析】有無人諗過一個好理性好客觀既原因，去分析香港街頭抗爭點解會停撚左？？？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2439001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2439001</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>誤導人攻擊吳志森：</ins><br />\n<br />\n吳志森：根據一分事實，講一分真話，反制BNO後會唔會跟住搞埋擁有雙重國籍嘅香港人？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390171</a><br />\n〖吳志森〗在權力面前，袁國勇可以再勇敢一些嗎？ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2344095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2344095</a><br />\n【吳志森引證】泛民生死存亡絕地反擊，以其輿論機器將本土派塑造為惡棍貪錢分化撚新敵人，並以受害者姿態翻盤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2170577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2170577</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>誤導人攻擊蘋果日報：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【Fake News盡在蘋果？】袁弓夷 節目Partner 何良懋，親身說法被蘋果老屈國會聽證會言論，搞到返唔到香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2283489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2283489</a><br />\n如果蘋果MPF A1唔係問題，陶傑應該為抹黑黃營KOL蠢老鼠一事道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2441513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2441513</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>誤導人攻擊劉細良：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【警世】不分化不割蓆已輪為最新一輪黃營話語權爭奪戰中的愚民手段！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2434499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2434499</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>誤導人攻擊黃世澤：</ins><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒公報私仇,斷章取義,無知,無持續進修,恐懼無領導地位,過橋抽板,濫權,眷戀光環,彈起只係時勢,有做獨裁者潛質<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229581</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>收左 Order 邊個 KOL 訂閱量多就攻擊：</ins><br />\n<br />\n點睇兩大時事youtuber吳志森黃世澤，一個24萬訂閱另一個8萬，但平均收視倒撚返轉一個3萬幾另一個5萬UP？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2234734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2234734</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>同時又收錢幫支持國安法既 KOL 洗底：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【國際線=虛偽】神駒直線抽擊國際線對就侵就兇狠，拜登對華「策略性忍耐」就視而不見！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2388437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2388437</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">拉</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSOURCE:<br />\n#228 回覆 - 如果見到有通街都知係五毛/PR嘅狗隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rcLiBsX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rcLiBsX</a>"},{"pid":"b2f3ebae3c7267bbab6f61ad2d684426357a805c","tid":2414942,"uid":34178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366e6da1a3217554a1868da76e9d4e39288ad1c8","tid":2414942,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55c56b642e005059010fd336b49c13b0116ce0d","tid":2414942,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"仆街３８號你走啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n【連登仔鐘意食精神鴉片】黃世柒係連登過街老鼠，但係黃世柒既連登PR戶口【交加街38號】出PO一直過百過千正評！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2437134\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2437134</a>"},{"pid":"d6ed6bbc636e74c45ebcda378a4155e20091ece8","tid":2414942,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e55c56b642e005059010fd336b49c13b0116ce0d","tid":2414942,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"仆街３８號你走啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n【連登仔鐘意食精神鴉片】黃世柒係連登過街老鼠，但係黃世柒既連登PR戶口【交加街38號】出PO一直過百過千正評！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2437134\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2437134</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:12:43.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣改埋名做 五毛/分化撚 名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f791cff4f4d109e67f8beeac4c5ba7b459421b","tid":2414942,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5d5ac4671594c93f6de4aa45e718c5b52b242d3","tid":2414942,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"250bd8a8fe213b07c4f7446ae7fcacd668400e92","tid":2414942,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T21:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完，入過校台追 post 得交加街條懵撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">搬石頭張六常，PR 網軍專門發佈 BNO 假消息、分化 BNO 手足 及 國際線，見字勿回，感謝。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據如下：</ins><br />\n<br />\n====搬石頭張六常 [常駐：校園台]====<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/36383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/36383</a><br />\n<br />\nPOST 1: [時間已證明六常是對的] BNO 苦 主 後 悔 移 英 ： 返 唔 到 香 港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2385148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2385148</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用英國資薪水平，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實英國最低工資水平遠高於香港，而且藍白領工種之間工資差距水平極低，尊重不同行業。雖然稅收較香港高，但同時有全民醫療同退休保障，長遠生活成本較香港低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPOST 2: 如果你自問學歷差冇經驗冇錢冇乜體力又想要舒服日子，建議留返香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2387307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2387307</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用英國工作機會攻擊英國，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實現時英國失業率較香港低，因為封城反而帶旺部份行業需求，另外英國疫苗注射效率極高，長遠英國工作機會因為武肺問題消退及脫歐人口流失而大幅提升</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPOST 3: [勸世2] 英國滿歧視，移民屬不智<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2378847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2378847</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用外國人會歧視人攻擊英國，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實英國英國本身已經有大量第一二代移民，甚至國家重要官員唔少都係移民後代<br />\n最近英國更有大量協助港人既組織相繼成立：e.g. <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2405905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2405905</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 此人同時擔任分化國際線既工作<br />\n攬炒巴 + 重光團隊只係可有可無嘅人，炒作兩條蛋散係冇咩價值<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380384</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">拉</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSORUCE:<br />\n請問張六常(欣客)(狗隻#36383)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2325823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2325823</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHVHyF7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHVHyF7.png&h=ab7f4ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUU9dF9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUU9dF9.gif&h=173bb43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7e2yFme.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7e2yFme.gif&h=3a55c98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈毛就最叻架啦"},{"pid":"c2fe204a97d29d1b13caef946c23033972aa8b6b","tid":2414942,"uid":4526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload-hkgolden-media.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/upload.hkgolden.media/comment/5uxnyxtq.fqtbxjhcldl.trirlcegngx.03x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload-hkgolden-media.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2F5uxnyxtq.fqtbxjhcldl.trirlcegngx.03x.jpg&h=894c25ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7137817ced56c4d61ab1b2119b7bb9010428444f","tid":2414942,"uid":218082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:41:10.000Z","msg":"我頹問交加街38號點解椰子監都坐埋都係五毛<br />\n黃世柒條撚樣就放我入五毛list,屌佢老母爛牙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0f72f56a5ee420584c572c045ff021f4e42267","tid":2414942,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2fe204a97d29d1b13caef946c23033972aa8b6b","tid":2414942,"uid":4526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload-hkgolden-media.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/upload.hkgolden.media/comment/5uxnyxtq.fqtbxjhcldl.trirlcegngx.03x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload-hk